{"id":313758,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-各地上访维权者到医院探望刘凤刚牧师（/","date":"2013-09-16T17:34:41Z","modified":"2013-09-16T17:34:41Z","title":"维权网 | 各地上访维权者到医院探望刘凤刚牧师（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员陈旭报道）北京知名牧师刘凤刚因冠状动脉粥样硬化性心脏病，劳力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span><span>自发型心绞痛，陈旧性下壁心肌梗死，支架置入术后高血压病、高脂血症、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>型糖尿病等病非常严重，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日到北京阜外心血管医院北楼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">225</span><span>病区二楼住院。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘凤刚牧师在基督传道的同时，对弱势群体，特别是访民非常关心，经常在三九严寒之下和基督教会的弟兄到北京南站向访民分发衣物、食品；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年曾在其家中进行访民聚会。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年出狱后，刘凤刚牧师成立了访民培训班，向访民传授法律知识，普世价值；组织教会弟兄姐妹给访民发放食品、衣物。为此长期遭到当局骚扰，并多次被带到派出所喝茶。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>正因为刘凤刚牧师给予访民很多帮助，访民得知刘牧师住院的消息后，在下午三时允许探望的情况下，在京访民代表蔡志国、尹旭安、段淑兰、田玉英、郭红、阮积忠、龚登玉、沈立秀、吕动力等人到医院探望，为刘牧师带去最诚挚的祝福，祝刘牧师最日康复，回到自己最热爱的事业岗位，带来上帝的福音，照耀到人类。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>最后，因刘牧师可能要在医院呆一段时间，访民朋友们安排了一个看护表，并且从今晚开始执行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-jAN5u4AArHg/UjcLZnP6-CI/AAAAAAAAoRA/FIWv95mSvC0/s1600/CIMG0646.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-jAN5u4AArHg/UjcLZnP6-CI/AAAAAAAAoRA/FIWv95mSvC0/s320/CIMG0646.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HPuEvQMoGzI/UjcLXzH_OFI/AAAAAAAAoQ4/r_4CV0FbpCI/s1600/CIMG0648.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HPuEvQMoGzI/UjcLXzH_OFI/AAAAAAAAoQ4/r_4CV0FbpCI/s320/CIMG0648.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4Nvq1xCesVk/UjcLbLPP3ZI/AAAAAAAAoRI/HXJmuxUUYyU/s1600/CIMG0651.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4Nvq1xCesVk/UjcLbLPP3ZI/AAAAAAAAoRI/HXJmuxUUYyU/s320/CIMG0651.JPG\" width=\"280\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}